  "text": "In this study, we found a positive relationship of high triglyceride with hyperuricemia in both men and women, in agreement with an Indian study [CITATION_1] . Dietary habits have been changing in both China and India, and obesity and hypertriglyceridemia have begun to occur in younger people.",
